title: Corner One Bedroom, Unmatched Amenities, 24 hour Concierge Service!
posting_body: ['Welcome to Miro', 'Miro reflects the dynamic, multi-faceted character of contemporary life.', 'Start your day with a boost of energy at the fitness center, hone in on work from the comfortable co-working lounges, and wrap up the evening soaking up tranquility from the rooftop sky deck.', 'Come home to the perfect blend of easy relaxation, bold design, and quality finishes.', 'Live beyond your expectations.', 'Amenities Include:', 'Swimming Pool', 'Contemporary European Cabinetry', 'Private Co-Working Spaces', 'Six West – Acoustic Studio', 'Fire Pit', 'Private Screening Room', 'Social Co-Working Lounge NOW OPEN', 'Capacious Closets', 'Exclusive Rooftop Demonstration Kitchen', 'Private Game Lounge', 'Expansive Balconies', 'Fitness Deck & Yoga Studio NOW OPEN', 'Call:', 'show contact info', 'For more information, visit us at: <URL>', '*Pricing and availability are subject to change daily.', 'Photos may not be of the exact advertised unit.', 'Please contact us today for the most up to date information!']
